models\n+\n+Decay f'_0 # Edited by U. Tamponi, October 2016\n+0.1357   pi+  pi-                        PHSP;\n+0.0678   pi0  pi0                        PHSP;\n+0.3783   pi+ pi+ pi- pi-                 PHSP; # Approximation of several 2 broad mesons amplitudes\n+0.3783   pi+ pi- pi0 pi0                 PHSP; # Approximation of several 2 broad mesons amplitudes\n+0.0111   K+   K-                         PHSP;\n+0.0055  K_S0  K_S0                       PHSP;\n+0.0055   K_L0  K_L0                      PHSP;\n+0.0018  eta eta                          PHSP;\n+Enddecay\n+\n+Decay f_1 # Checked by U. Tamponi, october 2016. No changes are needed\n+0.110000000 rho0    pi+     pi-                             PHSP;\n+0.043364159 rho0    pi0     pi0                             PHSP;\n+0.043442860 rho+    pi-     pi0                             PHSP;\n+0.043442860 rho-    pi+     pi0                             PHSP;\n+0.094440999 a_00    pi0                                     VSS;\n+0.094440999 a_0+    pi-                                     VSS;\n+0.094440999 a_0-    pi+                                     VSS;\n+0.086570916 eta     pi+     pi-                             PHSP;\n+0.043285458 eta     pi0     pi0                             PHSP;\n+0.020226114 K+      K-      pi0                             PHSP;\n+0.010152407 K0      anti-K0 pi0                             PHSP;\n+0.020226114 anti-K0 K+      pi-                             PHSP;\n+0.020226114 K0      K-      pi+                             PHSP;\n+0.055000000 gamma   rho0                                    PHSP;\n+0.220000000 pi0     pi0     pi+     pi-                     PHSP;\n+0.000000000 pi+     pi+     pi-     pi-                     PHSP;\n+0.000740000 phi     gamma                                   PHSP;\n+Enddecay\n+\n+# Edited by U. Tamponi, October 2016\n+# Reverted to the Belle DECAY table, which is coherent with PDG 2015 infos\n+Decay f'_1\n+0.2000   K*+  K-                         VVS_PWAVE 1.0 0.